quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  41,9,"Bagambe nti abaffe mmwe muwakanya oyo eyatonda ensi mu nnaku bbiri nemumuteekako ebisinzibwa ebirala, oyo (gwe mukola ebyo) ye mulezi w'ebitonde"
  41,10,"Era yassa mu yo (ensi) ensozi nga asinziira ku ngulu kwayo, (olwo nno nezikka wansi) era naagissaamu omukisa era yagererera mu yo ebyokulya byayo (ebiriibwa ebiramu byonna ebigirimu, ebyo byonna yabimalira) mu nnaku nnya, (ekyo kye kyokwanukula) ekituufu eri ababuuza"
  41,11,"Oluvanyuma yadda ku kukola eggulu nga nalyo (mu kusooka) lyali mukka, olwo nno naligamba n'ensi, nti mujje okwagala n'obutayagala, byombi nebigamba nti tuzze nga tugonze"
  41,12,"Olwo naagamaliriza nga gali eggulu musanvu mu nnaku bbiri, naalagira mu buli ggulu ne mussibwamu ebintu byamu era netuwunda eggulu eririraanye ensi n’amataala n’abakuumi, okwo nno kugera kwa nantakubwa ku mukono, omumanyi ennyo"
  41,13,Singa bawuguka (nebatakukkiriza) bagambe nti mbatiisizza ebibonerezo ebikakali okufaanana nga ebibonerezo ebyatuuka ku bantu ba A-adi ne Thamud
  41,14,"Mu kiseera ababaka bwe baabajjira nga babava mu maaso ne mabega waabwe nga bagamba nti, temusinzanga okugyako Katonda (abatakkiriza) ne bagamba nti singa Mukama omulabirizi waffe yayagala (kututumira) yandiisizza Malayika n’olwekyo mazima ffe tuwakanya ebyo bye mutumiddwa nabyo"
  41,15,"Bo abantu ba A-adi anti beekuza mu nsi mu butali butuufu, era nebagamba nti ani atusinga amaanyi? abaffe baali tebakiraba nti mazima Katonda oyo eyabatonda, yye yaabasinga amaanyi. Okukola ekyo baali bawakanya obubonero bwaffe"
  41,16,"Netubasindikira kibuyaga owamaanyi mu nnaku ezaali zijjudde ebizibu tulyoke tubakombese ku bibonerezo ebyobuswavu mu bulamu obwensi, so nga ate ebibonerezo by'enkomerero bye bisinga okuswaza era bo tebagenda kutaasibwa"
  41,17,"Bo aba Thamud twabalaga ekkubo ly'obulungamu naye bo nebakulembeza obwamuzibe ku bulungamu, olwo nno okubwatuka kwe bibonerezo ebinyomesa ne kubatuukako olwebyo bye baakolanga"
  41,18,Era twawonya abakkiriza era nga baali batya Katonda